Package: anybadger
Type: Package
Title: Create Project Badges from R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lorenzo Meninato
Maintainer: Lorenzo Meninato <lorenzomeninato@gmail.com>
Description: Create Project Badges from R
    This project was inspired by the anybadge library in python.
    You can use this package to create custom badges in a standard svg format.
    This is useful for a company to use internally, where it may not be possible
    to create badges through external providers.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    fastmap,
    memoise,
    R6,
    glue,
    purrr,
    config
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
